import {
  GridItem,
  Heading,
  Text,
  Box,
  SimpleGrid,
  Center,
  Stack,
  Spacer,
} from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

import AspectCard from './AspectCard'
import AspectCardJalaine from './AspectCardJalaine'
import AspectCardMariela from './AspectCardMariela'
import AspectCardBruce from './AspectCardBruce'

function Homepage() {
  return (
    <>
      <GridItem colStart={1} colSpan={4}>
        <Center>
          <Box maxW='36rem'>
            <Heading mb={4}>Classical Maya Civilization </Heading>
            <Stack direction={'row'}>
              <Text fontSize='xl'>The Golden Age of the Maya</Text>

              <Spacer />
              <Text
                fontSize={'inherit'}
                fontWeight={'light'}
                color={'orange.400'}
              >
                {' '}
                250 - 900 C.E.
              </Text>
            </Stack>
          </Box>
        </Center>
        <SimpleGrid columns={{ xl: 1, lg: 2, sm: 1 }} spacing={3}>
          <AspectCard />
          <AspectCardJalaine />
          <AspectCardMariela />
          <AspectCardBruce />
        </SimpleGrid>
      </GridItem>
    </>
  )
}

export default Homepage
